overview: Leena and her friends get up to all sorts of high jinks at a bachelor party before Leena is miraculously transformed into a 50 foot woman. She then decides to take revenge on all the men in her life who have abused her. Two versions were released for the home video market: an 88 minute hardcore version and a 60 minute softcore version.
tagline: Leena's back, in a very BIG way...
title: Attack of the 50 Foot Hooker
